channel.title: How good is aryan these days?
channel.description:
For some reason in the last few days, I've been such a noob. Anyways:
I havn't used aryan since a month or two before the mass ban. And with sbot3 taken down, my friend can't afford to pay for our server, plus I already owe him a few hundred dollars. So I am planning on dusting off aryan, and start using it again to get some cash.
The last time I used it, I was able to make all 12 accounts last for nearly a month, and I'd be making a few mill a day. I doubt it's gonna go like that anymore, so I thought I'd ask, how long do your accounts last for, if your not using a proxy or anything? Or basically I need to be a bit more informed on aryan again, since I havnt used it for so many month's. If someone could point me in the right direction like a tutorial on using the proxies, or anything else I'm going to need, that would be much appreciated =)
